283
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:37,570
If it was with you...

284
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:55,650
I suppose

285
00:22:57,460 --> 00:23:01,590
you're really a prince.

286
00:23:03,420 --> 00:23:05,020
Huh?

287
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:10,000
You always treat me

288
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:13,050
like I'm special.

289
00:23:17,710 --> 00:23:20,720
I don't know if

290
00:23:24,060 --> 00:23:26,590
I should be thanking you.

291
00:23:35,950 --> 00:23:38,210
[Win]

292
00:23:39,100 --> 00:23:41,360
If I get this

