[Kenno High School]

296
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,850
It's cold.

297
00:24:26,890 --> 00:24:27,810
You know...

298
00:24:27,810 --> 00:24:29,510
- I...
- I...

299
00:24:30,340 --> 00:24:32,080
- Go ahead.
- Go ahead.

300
00:24:39,290 --> 00:24:44,020
I thought I would confess.

301
00:24:48,420 --> 00:24:50,110
So did I.

302
00:24:55,540 --> 00:25:02,870
I guess we decided to be brave.

303
00:25:03,660 --> 00:25:07,470
We should have done this sooner.

